In this version, we created the basic part of the project. We made an Airport class with code, location, and Schengen status. We added functions to: load airports from a file, add and remove airports, check if an airport is in Schengen. We created a plot (Schengen vs non-Schengen airports), a map in Google Earth and we built a simple interface (Tkinter) so users can use all features easily.
